                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120115-43-off243 t18120115-43-cd244"></join>, a bag, value 2 d. seven dollars, eleven three shilling bank tokens, eleven eighteen-penny bank tokens, and six shillings, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18120115-43-victim478" type="victimName">
